** For master node **

curl -sfL -H 'Pragma: no-cache' https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lblanc/k8s/main/ubuntu-22.04.1/install-k8s-master.sh | sh -


** For worker nodes **

curl -sfL -H 'Pragma: no-cache' https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lblanc/k8s/main/ubuntu-22.04.1/install-k8s-worker.sh | sh -

** For join worker nodes **

curl -sfL -H 'Pragma: no-cache' https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lblanc/k8s/main/ubuntu-22.04.1/join-worker-nodes.sh | sh -